Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:05.75,Show_Title,Title sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H292A2F&\bord0}{My }{\1a&HFF&\bord1\3c&HA183CA&}{T}{\3c&H000000&}{iny }{\bord0\1a&H00&}{Senpai}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:08.83,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{We've got an emergency here}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.61,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Are you paying attention, me?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:17.84,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{There's someone other than me \Ndancing around inside of my heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:20.09,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{I want to talk to her}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:23.14,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{I want to touch her}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:28.63,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Look, I get it, but for now try to pipe down}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.86,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{What in the world am I doing?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:34.61,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{You're right next to me}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:40.86,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{And this is the perfect chance...}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:42.44,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{HONEY}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.44,0:01:47.15,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{I'm trapped by that sweet rich taste}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:50.36,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{And I don't think I can ever escape}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:52.86,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{I may as well just sink into it}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:53.67,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{HONEY}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:58.47,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{It's another day in your dazzling presence}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.47,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{We may never be \Non the same page with this love but}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:07.90,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Oh, I love you so much, I just have to laugh}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.49,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,{What are you up to, Hayakawa-san?}Em làm gì thế Hayakawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:31.71,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Y-You've got the wrong person! \NI-I'm not Hayakawa, Manager!}A-Anh nhầm người rồi, em không \Nphải Hayakawa, quản lý!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.50,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You just called me your manager.}Em vừa gọi quản lý kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.88,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\c&H8F6C6D&\b1\3c&HFCFFFC&\shad0\}{Cosplay Event Reception\NOn the Left}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:35.88,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Of all the people...}Trong tất cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:42.14,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{The manager is like the textbook \Ndefinition of a normie, too!}Quản lý là người bình thường nhất nữa chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:48.77,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Huh. A cosplay event? I see.}Sự kiện cosplay à?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:50.54,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-san.}Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:51.77,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes?}Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.55,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Where do you buy an outfit like that?}Em mua bộ đó ở đâu thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:58.63,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{W-Well, I-I actually made it myself.}E-Em tự may!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.28,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I'm done.}Xong phim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:03.10,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{It's all over for me...}Kết thúc rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:05.26,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{He's probably wondering \Nwhy a grown woman is doing}Anh ấy sẽ thắc mắc tại sao một phụ nữ trưởng thành
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:07.29,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{something like this and thinks it's creepy.}lại làm cái trò này và nghĩ rằng nó thật kì lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.79,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I have to say, Hayakawa-san...}Cơ mà Hayakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.15,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Here it comes! The words every otaku dreads!}Đến rồi! Những từ ngữ mọi otaku đều sợ!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:16.30,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I don't wanna hear it! I don't wanna \Nhear my manager call me creepy!}Mình không muốn nghe quản lý nói kì lạ đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:19.92,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{That's pretty cool, Hayakawa-san.}Nó khá ngầu đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:24.46,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{It is?}Vậy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:26.93,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I think it's really cool.}Ừ, tôi nghĩ thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:35.69,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{Wait, how?! What about this is cool?}Hả? Chỗ nào? Ngầu chỗ nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.88,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Your approach to life, maybe?}Cách em sống?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.32,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{A-All that?!}C-Cách sống?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.30,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I don't have any hobbies,}Tôi không có sở thích nào cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:45.48,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{so I respect people who do, \Nlike you. I think it's pretty cool.}Nên nhìn những người như em, tôi rất ngưỡng mộ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:52.73,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Then again, that outfit \Nis more cute than cool.}Và bộ dạng này, dễ thương lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:58.21,Italics,Hayakwawa,0,0,0,,{How can he just up and say \Nsomething like that?!}S-Sao anh ấy lại thản nhiên nói\N dễ thương nhẹ nhàng vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:00.27,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:02.97,Main,Haykawa,0,0,0,,{N-Nothing, th-thank you.}K-Không có gì ạ. Cảm ơn anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.64,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Manager! Please don't tell anyone about this.}Quản lý! Anh đừng kể ai nghe chuyện này!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.19,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Is it supposed to be a secret?}Không được kể hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:11.52,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Please!}Làm ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.77,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{But it's really impressive.}Nhưng nó tuyệt mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:16.42,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{That's a matter of opinion.}Vấn đề không phải chỗ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:17.77,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,T-Tóm lại...{A-Anyway...}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:23.28,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{Let's keep this a secret, \Njust between us. Please.}Xin hãy giữ bí mật chuyện này.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.04,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Cute!}Dễ thương quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:29.32,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Why would you say it again?!}Tại sao anh lại khen nữa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.54,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Well...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:35.01,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{The first one was more about \Nyour costume and how you look,}Lần đầu là bộ dạng và trang phục của em,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:38.42,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{and the second one was more about \Nyou personally, Hayakawa-san.}lần thứ 2 là về tính cách đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:43.12,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I didn't want an actual explanation!}Em không cần nghe anh giải thích!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:45.93,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I didn't hear anything \Nyou just said! Not a thing!}Em chưa nghe gì cả! Không nghe thấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:48.17,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{But it's true that you're—}Nhưng sự thật là em--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:49.53,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Like! I! Said!}Em đã bảo là!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:53.62,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I heard nothing!}Em không nghe gì cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.69,Sign_Basic,Word Balloon sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H8C8F8D&\fnArial\shad0\3c&HFCFFFC&\fs16\pos(408,52.666)\frz283.1}{I love you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:05.49,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{The deadline for Comiket \Nsubmissions is coming up...}Hạn chót của Comiket lần này sắp đến rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.99,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{But I can't focus.}Nhưng mình không thể tập trung.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:12.55,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I can't believe my boss \Nfound out that I'm a cosplayer.}Không thể tin là quản lý phát hiện ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:16.89,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I asked him to keep quiet, \Nand I doubt he'd blab, but...}Mình đã nhờ anh ấy giữ bí mật và cũng đồng ý nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:20.67,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I wonder if there's a pressure point \Nto erase someone's memory...}Không biết có huyện nào xoá kí ức không nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.01,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Where am I? What are you?}Tôi là ai? Đây là đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:26.57,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{How did this even happen?}Sao chuyện này lại xảy ra chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:30.76,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Work is going to be a nightmare tomorrow.}Ngày mai đi làm nặng nề quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:33.39,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai!}Chị ơi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:37.64,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'd like you to review the materials I put \Ntogether for the upcoming project submission.}Em muốn chị xem qua tài liệu\N em đã chuẩn bị cho kế hoạch lần này.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:39.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sure! I'll take a look.}Rồi! Để chị xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.39,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Let's see here...}Xem nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:45.10,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yep, you covered \Nyour bases nicely! Well done.}Ừm, em đã làm rất đầy đủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:46.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Th-Thank you.}C-Cảm ơn chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:49.52,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Didn't get anywhere with my manuscript...}Cuối cùng bản thảo vẫn chưa xong...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:50.92,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Didn't sleep much...}Không ngủ được...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:52.61,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{This really sucks...}Tệ quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:55.91,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa. Hey, Hayakawa?}Hayakawa? Này Hayakawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:59.64,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You okay? You look worn out.}Cậu ổn chứ? Trông mệt mỏi vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:02.29,Main,Haykawa,0,0,0,,{Oh, er, I-I'm totally fine!}À không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:06.97,Main,Haykawa,0,0,0,,{It's just, a bunch of stuff happened \Nyesterday... and I didn't get much sleep.}Chỉ là hôm qua nhiều chuyện quá nên thiếu ngủ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:10.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{A lack of sleep can contribute \Nto all kinds of health problems.}Thiếu ngủ ảnh hưởng đến sức khoẻ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:11.64,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Be careful, okay?}Nhớ cẩn thận nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:15.88,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{When you can't sleep, try counting cats!}Khi không ngủ được, em thử đếm mèo xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:17.50,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{One kitty,}Một mèo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.10,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{two kitties,}Hai mèo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.76,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{three kitties,}Ba mèo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:22.76,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I think most people use sheep...}Em nghĩ bình thường là đếm cừu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.58,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{four kitties—}Bốn mèo--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.61,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{No! Cats are fine, too.}Không không! Mèo cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:29.19,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Thanks for the concern, Katase-san.}Cảm ơn vì đã lo cho em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:30.79,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-san...}Hayakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:33.91,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Are you not feeling well? Everything okay?}Em không khoẻ hả? Mọi chuyện ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.54,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{M-Manager?!}Q-Quản lý?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:40.79,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Uh, well... er... yes, I-I'm okay.}À vâng... E-em ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:45.80,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Okay. In that case, would you like to \Njoin me for dinner tonight?}Rồi, vậy tối nay đi ăn với tôi không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:48.52,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I was hoping we could talk.}Chúng ta cần nói chuyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.16,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{In a nice, quiet restaurant.}Là một nhà hàng khá tuyệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:53.30,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Just the two of us,\Nif that's all right.}Chỉ hai chúng ta thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:57.56,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Dinner for j-just the two of us?! \NYou mean like...}Ăn tối chỉ có 2 người? Tức là...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:01.48,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,Dễ thương... dễ thương lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.35,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{W-Well...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.23,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{a-as long as we're done before the last train.}m-miễn là em bắt kịp chuyến tàu cuối...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.42,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,May quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:11.21,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Let me know when\Nyou're done work.}Khi nào xong việc nói tôi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:13.54,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.40,Main,Shioiri,0,0,0,,{Is this a date?}Hẹn hò à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:16.74,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I-It isn't!}K-Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sounds suspicious!}Mờ ám ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.87,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Well, it's not!}Không có mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.32,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Right.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:25.59,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{This isn't a date or anything like that.}Không phải hẹn hò gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:33.22,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{My boss just... asked me out... \Nfor a bit of dinner.}Cấp trên...mời đi ăn bình thường thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:35.93,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{It's nothing.}Không có gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.22,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{It's not a big deal!}Không có vấn đề gì hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:42.46,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Sorry about the wait.}Xin lỗi vì để anh chờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:50.57,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You okay?}Em ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.98,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{W-Well... er...}À vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.63,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Thanks for the save.}Cảm ơn anh ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:58.72,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Don't mention it. Watch your step, now.}Đừng lo. Nhớ cẩn thận đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:07:59.37,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:04.50,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Speaking of... when you came for your \Nemployment test, didn't you break a heel?}Cơ mà hình như lúc\N phỏng vấn em cũng làm gãy guốc nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:08.13,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{You remember that?}Anh vẫn còn nhớ ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.26,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Of course I do.}Nhớ chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.26,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{That must've been rough.}Hẳn phải khó khăn lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:21.77,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{But I'm glad you passed, \Nand now we get to work together.}Nhưng thật may khi em đậu và giờ chúng ta làm chung.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.62,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{He remembered...}Anh ấy vẫn nhớ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:27.02,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Now, let's get a move on, Hayakawa-san.}Nào, đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.27,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{O-Okay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:34.64,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I'd think you're used to the office by now,}Có vẻ em đã quen với công ty mình rồi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:37.24,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{but do you have any issues \Nor things you're worried about?}nhưng có vấn đề gì lo lắng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:41.26,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{No. Everyone is really nice, \Nso nothing comes to mind.}Không ạ. Mọi người đều tuyệt vời.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:43.32,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Well, that's good to hear.}Vậy à, tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:45.34,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{The section chief mentioned \Nhow impressed he was}Trưởng bộ phận khá ấn tượng
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:46.93,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{with how much faster you've gotten.}khi thấy em làm việc rất nhanh đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:49.13,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Come on, it's nothing that impressive.}Không có gì ấn tượng đâu ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:54.22,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{All he's brought up \Nduring dinner is work stuff,}Trong khi ăn mà anh ấy cũng nói về công việc,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:57.14,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{so I guess this is more like \Na dinner meeting than anything.}có vẻ đây chỉ là cuộc gặp gỡ thông thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:02.25,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Manager, didn't you mention \Nsomething you wanted to discuss?}Quản lý, chuyện anh muốn nói với em là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:04.14,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Right.}À phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:07.15,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-san...}Hayakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:11.39,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I know this might surprise you \Ncoming out of the blue, but...}Tôi biết đột nhiên nói thế này có hơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:17.41,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-san...}Hayakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:22.44,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{when I look at you, I got really excited.}khi nhìn em, tôi thấy thổn thức.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:27.50,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I've never felt this way before,}Tôi chưa từng gặp cảm giác này bao giờ,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:31.42,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{and I'm not sure if it's fair \Nto spring this on you...}và không biết là mình có say không...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:37.32,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Hang on... is this... is he...?!}Khoan đã... vậy tức là... anh ấy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:40.43,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-san!}Hayakawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:42.51,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes?!}V-Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:47.02,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I'd like to attend a cosplay event with you!}Tôi cũng muốn tham gia sự kiện cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:52.59,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I mean, when I think about \Nhow you made that costume,}Thì cái bộ quần áo em làm đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:55.50,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I get excited thinking about \Nhow much fun it must be!}Tôi trở nên thổn thức khi nghĩ về nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:57.03,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{That's what you meant?!}Ý anh là vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:00.84,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Well... are you saying you \Nwant to cosplay, too, Manager?}Anh nói rằng muốn cosplay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:03.77,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Nope. When I went home \Nand started looking into it,}Không. Khi về nhà và tìm hiểu nó,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:07.50,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I found out about photo sessions \Nthey have for cosplay, and well...}thì thấy có mấy album chụp cosplay, nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.44,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I'd love to capture your exploits with this!}Tôi muốn chụp em bằng thứ này!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:13.05,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{What a scary combo of initiative \Nand purchasing power!}Tiềm lực tài chính và quyết tâm thật đáng sợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:17.24,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I-I mean, you could just take pictures \Nof whatever cosplay you want.}A-Anh thích thì cứ chụp thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.47,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{You don't need me for that...}Cần gì đến em...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:23.62,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{But you were the one who made me \Nrealize it'd be fun, Hayakawa-san.}Nhưng em là người giúp tôi nhận ra nó, Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:27.08,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I want it to be you.}Tôi muốn chụp em.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:34.07,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{It's not fair how he can just say stuff \Nlike that with a straight face...}Thật bất công khi thẳng thắn như vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.46,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{The month after next,}Tháng sau nữa,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:43.64,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{there's going to be an event \Nat the same location, so if you want...}sẽ có sự kiện tương tự ở chỗ đó, nếu anh muốn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:49.44,Main - Top,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Oh, but in exchange, you need the check out \Nthe things my costumes are from!}Nhưng đổi lại, anh hãy \Nkiểm tra trang phục cho em nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.83,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,0)\pos(374,344)\fnComic Sans MS\b1\fsp2\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0}{Real otaku always proselytize}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.83,Main - Top,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Otherwise you can't take pictures!}Nếu không thì khỏi chụp ảnh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:54.68,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Cute.}Dễ thương quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:55.98,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{How?!}Tại sao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:57.84,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{None of that was cute at all!}Không có gì dễ thương cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:01.40,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Yes, it was. The way you're so earnest \Nabout talking about the things you like.}Có chứ! Nhìn thấy em cố gắng hết\N sức và nghiêm túc về chuyện đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:02.56,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{It was very c—}Cách em nói về nó--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:04.51,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{No more explanations!}Không cần anh giải thich!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.72,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{But you're the one who was—}Nhưng em hỏi--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:09.15,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I do not want to hear it at all! \NNot another word!}EM không có hỏi gì cả! Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.87,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki, you wanna grab lunch?}Shinozaki, ăn trưa không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.89,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sure. Let me just finish this up.}Ờ, mà phải xong cái này đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:19.83,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Got it.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:22.24,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You need to talk?}Muốn nói gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:26.24,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Well... yeah.}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:30.36,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Okay, one sec. I'll be right there.}Chờ chút nhé. Để làm xong đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:32.62,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I'll wait in the lobby.}Tớ chờ ở sảnh nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:37.55,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Y'know, Hayakawa-san and Shinozaki-kun \Nseem closer than regular coworkers.}Hayakawa và Shinozaki có vể thân nhau nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:40.75,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Apparently, they're childhood friends \Nwho grew up as neighbors.}Thì hai đứa là bạn thuở nhỏ lại hàng xóm nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:43.11,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Oh, right. I remember \Nhearing about that, now.}À hình như có nghe qua.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:47.08,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Are you interested in what's going on?}Anh tò mò hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:49.21,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Katase-san, there's no need to get giddy.}Katase à, em không cần trưng cái mặt đó ra đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:52.64,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Since you always pick on me, \NI'm just glad for a chance at payback!}Lúc nào anh chả chọc em, đây là cơ hội trả đũa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:58.55,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-san might've denied it before, \Nbut maybe there is actually a chance...}Hayakawa hồi trước phủ định, nhưng có lẽ nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:03.28,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.40,0:12:03.28,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(536.5,119)\fnComic Sans MS\an5\b1\fs24\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0}{Or the\Nreunited\Nchildhood\Nfriends/\Nclassmates\Nromance.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:03.28,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{A reunited childhood \Nfriends/classmates romance.}Sự tái hợp của bạn thuở nhỏ, bạn cùng lớp.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.28,0:12:06.66,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fntimes new roman\an5\b1\fs24\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0\pos(102.598,205.6)}{The age-gap\Nromance\Nbetween\Na senpai\Nand kohai\Nat work.}Tình cảm giữa \Nđàn chị và đàn em\N trong công ty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.66,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{An age-gap romance \Nbetween a senpai and kohai at work.}Tình cảm giữa đàn chị và đàn em trong công ty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:10.10,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Which one am I supposed to root for?!}Anh sẽ phải ủng hộ ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:13.29,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sh-Sh-Shinozaki-san and I aren't like that...}S-Shinozaki không nghĩ về em như thế đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.92,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{More importantly, Manager!}Cơ mà quản lý!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:18.55,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Aren't you forgetting an option?}Anh quên còn lựa chọn khác à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.80,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Another option...?}Lựa chọn khác...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:24.48,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{There's nothing like another girl.}Quả nhiên yuri là số một.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:26.65,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{H-Hayakawa-san...}H-Hayakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:28.03,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Of course.}Dĩ nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:30.06,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Why would you take it that way?!}Tại sao lại như thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:33.02,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You brought it up, Katase-san,}Cơ mà em nữa Katase...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:36.84,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{but aren't you curious about what's going on \Nwith Shinozaki-kun and Hayakawa-san?}em không tò mò chuyện\N giữa Shinozaki với Hayakawa à.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:41.61,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{N-Not really. The two of them \Ncan be as friendly as they want...}K-Không hẳn. Hai đứa thân thiết thì liên quan gì em...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:45.66,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{B-Besides, why would I care?}V-Với cả tại sao em phải quan tâm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.68,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I dunno, why would you?}Tại sao nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:50.91,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Aw! Don't answer a question \Nwith another question!}Đừng có trả lời bằng một câu hỏi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:54.99,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Come on, we better hurry before \Nthe lunch crowds fill everywhere up!}Thôi nào, đi nhanh trước khi nhà ăn chật kín người!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:56.27,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{But why would you?!}Nhưng tại sao nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Manager!}Quản lý!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:02.20,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{The manager found out you're an otaku?}Quản lý phát hiện cậu là otaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:03.51,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I got careless.}Tớ đã bất cẩn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:05.18,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{How'd that even happen?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:07.58,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Did he see something you were drawing...?}Anh ấy thấy cậu vẽ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:10.43,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Not exactly.}Không hẳn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:15.19,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki knows I'm an otaku, \Nbut not about the cosplay stuff.}Shinozaki biết mình là otaku\N nhưng không biết vụ cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:19.31,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I don't really think him knowing \Nis a problem, though.}Tớ nghĩ anh ấy không có vấn đề gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:23.57,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Well... maybe not a big problem...}À thì cũng đúng...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.25,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Not a serious one, but...}Không có gì nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:29.57,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,{Cute... Cute... Cute...}Dễ thương... dễ thương... dễ thương...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.87,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{If it's not a problem, then what's the issue?}Không có vấn đề thì thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:34.83,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{You're right.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:38.70,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I guess I should be glad \Nhe didn't see me drawing BL dojinshi.}Cũng may anh ấy không biết tớ vẽ BL.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.17,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Whacha talking about?}Mấy đứa nói chuyện gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.46,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{M-Manager?!}Q-Quản lý?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:44.46,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Did he hear all that?!}Anh ấy nghe thấy rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:47.34,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Are you here for lunch with Senpai?}Hai người đến ăn trưa ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:49.21,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Are you curious?}Tò mò không em?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:53.60,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Not exactly... and why are you \Ngrinning like that?}Không hẳn... cơ mà sao anh nhìn nham nhở thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:56.73,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Do you mind if \Nwe join you for lunch?}Bọn chị ăn cùng được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:58.48,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Oh, sure.}À vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:02.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{In that case, I wanna sit \Nnext to Hayakawa-san!}Vậy chị muốn ngồi cạnh Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.23,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Không sao em à.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:07.49,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What is up with you today?!}Anh bị cái gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:10.08,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I wonder what I should get.}Chọn món gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:11.69,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I'm curious, Hayakawa-san.}Cơ mà Hayakawa nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:14.97,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{What's BL?}BL là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:19.56,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{W-Well, it's, er... it is sort of a...}À nó là... kiểu như là...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:24.07,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What's wrong, Hayakawa-san? \NYou've gone bright red.}Sao thế? Trông em có vẻ đỏ mặt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.01,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I-I-I wonder why.}E-E-Em không biết nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:30.78,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Is it okay if I make this picture \Nmy home screen background?}Anh để làm hình nền máy tính nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.07,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Of course not!}Không được!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:37.40,Main,Shiori/Eyecatch,0,0,0,,{\i1}{My Tiny Senpai}{\i0}{.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.38,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san!}Shinozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:50.24,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Trick or treat! \NHappy Halloween, Shinozaki-san!}Cho kẹo hay bị ghẹo? Chúc mừng Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:51.98,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai!}Chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:55.79,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's Halloween, after all.}Là Halloween mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:56.67,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What do you think?}Em thấy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:59.92,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's cu—er, very nice looking.}À nó dễ-- nhìn lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.82,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I was kinda surprised.}Em hết hồn luôn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:05.75,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That being the case, \Nonce again: trick or treat!}Thế nên là: Cho kẹo hay bị ghẹo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:10.26,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry, I didn't get anything ready...}X-Xin lỗi chị, em chưa chuẩn bị gì hết...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:12.83,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That's okay.}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:14.26,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Here you go!}Của em nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.41,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, thank yo—}A, cảm ơn chị--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:30.03,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{T-Trick or treat?}C-Cho kẹo hay bị ghẹo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.53,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Well done! Here you go.}Ừm, em làm tốt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.70,Main - Top,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Come on, don't treat me like a kid.}Đừng xem em như trẻ con nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:37.45,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{What are you grinning about? \NAnd with cat ears on.}Sáng giờ anh cười gì vậy? Lại còn tai mèo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.60,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Which one would you like?}Em thích loại nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:42.04,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Just thinking how this is going to be \None sugary Halloween!}Chỉ đang nghĩ về một Halloween ngọt ngào thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.73,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{By the way, Hayakawa-san.}Cơ mà Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.00,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Happy Halloween!}Chúc mừng Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:52.26,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Yep, I was right. Your cat-like \Nnature makes it a good fit.}Đúng thật, em hợp với tai mèo lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.17,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{And we match!}Đồ đôi nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:57.26,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{M-Manager! Wearing cat ears at work is...}Q-Quản lý! Đeo tai mèo trong giờ làm có hơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:16:00.27,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(325,340)\fntimes new roman\b1\fsp2\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0}{*Can't bring herself to take them off}Không đủ sức kháng cự
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:05.77,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{The trick to happiness is a bowl of candy!}Nhiều kẹo bánh vui ghê nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:07.85,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I love Halloween!}Chị thích Halloween lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.53,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's pretty great.}Đúng thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:13.13,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's not a good idea to \Noverindulge on sweets, though.}Nhưng ăn nhiều đồ ngọt quá không tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:15.78,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Right! It can cause all kinds of problems.}Vâng! Nó sẽ gây ra nhiều vấn đề sức khoẻ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:19.15,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But it's Halloween, so what can you do?}Nhưng là Halloween mà, chịu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:20.81,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{True.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:25.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That also applies to Christmas, Valentine's, \Nbirthdays, and Hinamatsuri.}Và Giáng sinh, Valentine, sinh nhật, lễ hội búp bê nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.68,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Agreed!}Phải nhỉ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:28.42,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That's a lot of exceptions!}Sao mà nhiều ngày thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:30.92,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai, did you try these chocolates?}Chị ăn socola này rồi hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:33.87,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Not yet.}Vẫn chưa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:36.18,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{They're pretty good. \NThey've got a more mature taste.}Chúng ngon lắm. \NCó loại vị của người trưởng thành nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{A mature taste?}Vị trưởng thành?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.01,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-Is she...?}C-Chị ấy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:50.90,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sh-She's waiting for me to \Nfeed her the chocolate?}Chị ấy muốn mình đút cho à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:53.16,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{But if I do that...}Nhưng nếu làm thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:17:00.16,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{M-My finger might touch Senpai's mouth!}T-Tay mình sẽ chạm vào miệng chị ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:06.04,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{But a chance like this...}Nhưng cơ hội này...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:12.84,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yoink.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:17.08,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Đáng tiếc, hết giờ nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.30,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yummy!}Ngon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:27.50,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm so stupid! I wasted my chance!}Mình ngu quá! Đánh mất cơ hội rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:29.08,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san...}Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:35.86,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I-I feel weirdly toasty now.}Không hiểu sao cơ thể chị lạ quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:40.24,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki, is there any candy left?}Shinozaki, còn kẹo không?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:43.24,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-shan! Hayakawa-shan!}Hayakawa! Hayakawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:49.23,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Smooch! Smooch! Smooch!}Chụt! Chụt! Chụt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.66,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{What's going on with Katase-san?}Katase bị gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.86,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Don't go!}Đừng đi mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:52.55,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She just had one of these chocolates...}Chị ấy ăn socola...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:53.51,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Chocolate?}Socola?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:56.01,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Oh, these have alcohol in them.}A, loại này có cồn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:59.42,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Who could get that drunk off \Nof one chocolate?}Ai lại say khi mới ăn có 1 viên chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:01.67,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Smooooch!}Chụt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.76,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Would someone please help me?!}Ai đó cứu tôi với!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.44,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Who would've guessed that \NKatase-san would turn}Cơ mà chị ấy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.12,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{into a kissing machine\Nwhen she gets drunk?}hôn như cái máy khi bị say à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.64,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{A kissing machine...}Máy hôn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:10.12,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Does that mean I've got a chance?!}Tức là mình sẽ có cơ hội!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:11.78,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san...}Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:16.03,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Uh, well, I—I wasn't thinking \Nanything naughty!}E-Em không nghĩ gì đáng ngờ đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.28,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{Stare...}Nhìn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.28,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Could you at least say something?}Anh nói gì đó đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:23.03,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,{Sorry, sorry!}Xin lỗi, xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:23.03,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Is that...}Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:24.99,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Manager! Manager!}Quản lý! Quản lý!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:27.61,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Manager...}Quản lý...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:29.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{To be honest, I...}Thực ra em...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{There's something I need to tell you.}Có chuyện muốn nói với anh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.44,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai! Senpai! Our manager \Ndoesn't photosynthesize.}Chị ơi! Quản lý không có quang hợp đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.84,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Over there, see?}Bên kia kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:41.88,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Đây nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:42.93,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{What's up?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Manager! Manager!}Quản lý quản lý!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:51.37,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Manager... the truth is, there's \Nsomething I need to tell you...}Quản lý... có chuyện em muốn nói...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:53.82,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Wait, is this going where I think it is?!}Khoan, không lẽ chuyện đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.61,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Are Senpai... and Manager going to...}Chị ấy và quản lý sẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:58.82,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{K-K-K-Kiss?!}H-H-Hôn nhau?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.40,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Manager...}Quản lý...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:08.08,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{No! Hold on, Senpai!}Khoan đã chị ơi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:16.04,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I am so, so grateful for the way that you \Nalways, always work so hard for us,}Em rất biết ơn vì anh luôn làm việc chăm chỉ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:18.19,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{and to get our work done!}Và em rất cảm kích!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:19.63,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She's bowing out of gratitude?!}Quỳ xuống cảm ơn?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.37,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Maybe it's less about kissing}Có lẽ cảm xúc của em ấy khi say
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:26.66,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{and more about her emotions \Ntowards people getting amplified?}được khuếch đại chứ không phải là thích hôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:29.46,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh bless you, bless you, God and Manager!}Cảm tạ, cảm tạ, thần quản lý.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:31.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Th-That might be it.}C-Có lẽ là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.90,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm partly glad, and partly disappointed...}May quá... Và cũng hơi thất vọng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:37.96,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Katase à, đàn em bên kia kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:39.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{My kohai?}Đàn em?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.91,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Kohai, Kohai!}Đàn em, đàn em!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:46.41,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Hang on! Finding out \Nhow she feels about me...}Khoan đã! Chị ấy nghĩ sao về mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:48.68,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-I'm not emotionally prepared for this!}M-Mình chưa chuẩn bị tinh thần!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:52.67,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{U-Uh, Senpai, I...}Chị, em...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.80,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Wha...?!}Cái...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:04.30,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Tears?!}Khóc?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:08.33,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-I'm so sorry! I know I'm always \Ncausing trouble for you, Senpai!}Em xin lỗi vì toàn gây rắc rối cho chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.56,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's not that.}Không phải!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:13.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You used to have no idea \Nwhat to do on your own,}Em đã từng không biết phải làm gì một mình,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:16.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{but you're so capable now...}nhưng giờ đã có thể tự lập...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:19.07,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It makes me really happy, as your senpai!}Nó làm chị vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:20.82,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{So she's my mom?}Chị là mẹ em à...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.07,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:27.33,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{if you do need help, \Nyou can always turn to me, okay?}Nếu cần giúp đỡ thì cứ nói chị nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:29.75,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Senpai...}C-Chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:34.51,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-I think I'm gonna get you some water! \NYou sit here and wait a sec!}E-Em đi lấy nước! Chị chờ ở đây nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:33.06,Main - Top,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Tasty.}Ngon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:36.08,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{'Kay!}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:36.08,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,{Nice.}Tuyệt vời.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:41.21,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{So Senpai thinks...}Vậy là chị ấy nghĩ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:44.72,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You used to have no idea \Nwhat to do on your own...}Em đã từng không biết phải làm gì một mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:49.47,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm a little disappointed, \Nbut I'm still glad.}Mình hơi thất vọng nhưng cũng vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:52.86,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Katase-san, Katase-san.}Katase, Katase.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:58.98,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{What do you think about Shinozaki-kun \Npersonally, and not as a coworker?}Em nghĩ thế nào về Shinozaki, \Nkhông phải tư cách đàn em trong công ty nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.06,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai, I've got your water.}Em mang nước đến đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:05.74,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san is...}Shinozaki là...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:13.20,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{When it comes to him... I'm not sure yet...}Khi nói đến em ấy... em cũng không rõ nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:18.57,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I thought I had her that time.}Có lẽ là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:21.50,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Never mind that! Could you \Nplease delete that picture?}Quan trọng hơn là anh mau xoá mấy bức ảnh đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:23.42,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Which one do you mean?}Bức ảnh nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:25.96,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{The one with Katase-san and I... y'know...}Bức em với chị Katase ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:26.87,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{This one?}Bức này á?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.28,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Hurry up and delete it!}Mau xoá nó đi mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:30.75,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Can I use it on my home screen?}Để anh cài làm ảnh nền.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:32.47,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{Of course not!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:50.14,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Bleary-eyed and not fully awake from a dream}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:55.04,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{I still can't bring myself \Nto drink that bitter coffee}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:59.52,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{So I sneakily toss in \Ntwo pinches of a sweet secret}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:03.74,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{And let it slowly spread throughout}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:08.70,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{There's a local bakery \Nthat's only open sometimes}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:13.59,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Where I once had some toast that glittered}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:18.09,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{What is it that makes it so satisfying?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.09,0:22:22.26,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Almost like magic}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:27.34,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{I find myself thinking about that kind of thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:33.03,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{How the small things can be the most precious}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.74,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Deep inside my heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.74,0:22:42.14,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{It's ever so bittersweet}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:47.13,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{"Just being around you is enough"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:51.08,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Becomes my mantra}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.08,0:22:53.37,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Baby like sugar}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:02.70,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Baby you're the sugar}
